additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: People suffering from perfume sensitivity should be cautious when using this product. Air fresheners do not replace good hygiene practices. May cause an allergic reaction in some individuals. PRECAUTIONS FOR USE: Use only as directed in well ventilated areas. Keep out of reach of children and pets. If medical advice is needed, have product container or label at hand. Always switch off at the socket before removing or inserting the fragrance refill. Do not place in an area where the diffuser may be susceptible to hard knocks. Always keep the bottle and diffuser in an upright position.
